00:08:27.870 --> 00:08:29.810
at pagkatapos ng bawat Seremonya ng Pagsamba sa Langit,

00:08:29.810 --> 00:08:30.730
Kanyang Kamahalan

00:08:31.920 --> 00:08:34.250
